  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2080010/extras/725ec8c29dc241320c57527c212071ce.avif?t=1731585089\" width=616 height=64 /></span><br>They Came From the Sky 2 is highly-addictive and fast paced arcade game wherein you take the role of one of the giant Alien robot with one and only one Mission:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2080010/extras/be3765862bdb9c614ca017953507cb79.avif?t=1731585089\" width=616 height=64 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2>A excellent <span class=\"bb_strike\">Family</span> Alien friendly coffee-break game!<br>Inspired by the legendary game from Amiga: <strong>Walker</strong> and old good <strong>Defender</strong><br>Simple controls and pure arcade action<br>Infinite replayability as you chase ever higher scores!<br>Plenty of delicious humans to abduct<br>Over 20 brutal enemy types like: Grandpa, Skateboard Kid, or disabled person on Wheelchair<br>50 Human hidden Artifacts waiting to be discovered :O<br>Unlock New Weapons and special abilities in the Tech-Lab<br>Handcrafted pixel graphics created with love<br>Great music by Kevin MacLeod<br>Full Xbox 360 controller support<br>Includes Steam Achievements<br>and of course, Elvises!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2080010/extras/df61f16df39a56c6e7bb374ef3659e6a.avif?t=1731585089\" width=616 height=64 /></span><br><br><br><strong>Warning</strong>: This game contains elements of PIXEL violence :O",
